---
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
import Wrapper from "@/components/fundations/containers/Wrapper.astro";
import Text from "@/components/fundations/elements/Text.astro";
---

<BaseLayout>
  <section class="py-24">
    <Wrapper variant="standard">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 space-y-8">

        <Text
          tag="h1"
          variant="displaySM"
          class="font-display font-medium"
        >
          Commercial Conditions
        </Text>
        <div class="prose prose-neutral max-w-none">
          
        <Text tag="p" variant="textSM" class="text-base-600">
          Last updated: February 2026
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          These Commercial Conditions govern the provision of services offered
          through the website https://madridlandingkit.com (the “Website”).
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          By purchasing or contracting any service through this Website, you
          agree to the terms set out below.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          1. Provider Information
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          The services offered on this Website are currently provided by an
          individual operating under the project name Madrid Landing Kit, based
          in Madrid, Spain.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          A legal entity may be incorporated in the future. If so, these
          Commercial Conditions will be updated accordingly.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Contact email: info@madridlandingkit.com
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          2. Description of Services
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Madrid Landing Kit provides informational, advisory, and support
          services related to immigration procedures and relocation to Spain.
        </Text>

       <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Services are provided on a best-efforts basis and do not constitute
          legal representation unless expressly stated otherwise.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          3. Prices and Taxes
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          All prices displayed on the Website are expressed in euros (€) unless
          stated otherwise.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Prices do not include VAT unless explicitly indicated. Where
          applicable, Spanish VAT (currently 21%) will be added.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          4. Payment Terms
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Payment is required in advance before the provision of any service.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Payments are processed through third-party providers. Madrid Landing
          Kit does not store payment card details.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          5. Refund Policy
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Due to the personalized nature of the services, refunds are not
          guaranteed once service delivery has begun.
        </Text>

     <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Refund requests may be evaluated on a case-by-case basis if no work
          has started.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          6. Client Obligations
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          The client is responsible for providing accurate and complete
          information necessary for the service.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Madrid Landing Kit is not responsible for delays or issues caused by
          incomplete or incorrect information.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          7. Limitation of Liability
        </Text>

       <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Madrid Landing Kit shall not be held liable for decisions made by
          public authorities or third parties.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Any potential liability shall be limited to the amount paid for the
          specific service contracted.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          8. Governing Law and Jurisdiction
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          These Commercial Conditions are governed by Spanish law.
        </Text>

       <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          Any disputes shall be submitted to the courts of Madrid, Spain, unless
          mandatory consumer protection rules provide otherwise.
        </Text>

        <Text tag="h2" variant="textLG" class="font-medium">
          9. Changes to These Conditions
        </Text>

        <Text tag="p" variant="textBase" class="text-base-700">
          These Commercial Conditions may be updated at any time. The latest
          version will always be available on this Website.
        </Text>

      </div>
    </Wrapper>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
